Package pds.label

Class Summary
PDSElement PDSElement is a class that contains a single definition or line as specified in the PDS Object Defnition Language (ODL).
PDSItem PDSItem is a class that descibes the location within a PDSLabel of one or more elements.
PDSLabel PDSLabel is a class that contians all information regarding a PDS label entity.
PDSUtil PDSUtil is a class that contains utility methods which are useful for working with instances of PDSLabel and PDS labeled products.
PDSValue PDSValue is a class that contains a value which can be associated with an element.
